{{Game | Name=Empyrion Galactic Survival | Guid=3030-50402 | Deck=Empyrion is a 3D open world, space survival adventure game. | ReleaseDate=2015-08-05 | Characters= | Concepts= | Developers= | Franchises= | Genres=Genres/Action_Adventure,Genres/First_Person_Shooter,Genres/Simulation | Locations= | Objects= | Platforms= | Publishers= | Games= | Themes=Themes/Sci_Fi }}
<div id='imageData' data-json='{"infobox":[],"background":[]}' /> Empyrion is newly up coming space survival game that will give players the chance to try and survive a dangerous universe both on planets and in space.
After crashing on an alien world players must construct a base with the basic elements available and survive the harsh environment, before building a spaceship of there very own and blasting off into the stars

